Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
