Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone\Nsomewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’ll see I’m always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
