Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,REUNION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, what did you call her just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my mother.\NYuito, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call her mother as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be tricked.\NThat is a image created by BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakana is a noble person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She is one of the design children\Nwho possessed the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was one of the design children?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the beacon of hope\Nto realize our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and Kasane,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,she is your loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\NWakana was your instructor, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But she died in a certain incident\Nin Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find happiness in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she escape Togetsu and meet\Nwith Yuito's father in Suoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps she was under Suoh's protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi knew this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew she was connected to Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is surprising.\N-This is a little hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To beckon the two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this is the best form I should take.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and Kasane, you both understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the crisis brought about\Nby the expanding Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your help is needed to save\Nthe world from annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I'm sorry I left you\Nwhen you were just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will make up for your loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, do you still remember the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, all of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,People of the world are just like that puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you listen to my wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use my mother for your own plotting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to eliminate the whole world\Nalong with the history of those immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother would never want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After we retrieved the brain\Nof your beloved Wakana,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she had already become part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it mean BABE is\Nintegrated with human brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom didn't die in an Other attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She died because of BABE and Togetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the world's salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the salvation nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You only say that because\Nyou get to profit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never use my mother\Nto sway our resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are trying to stop us from moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to tarnish my mother's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Kunad Gate just expand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!\NThis place is collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu have finally shown their true color.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, there seems to be\Na teleportation point somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing else except for this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito!\N-I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Everyone is fine.\N-That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we won't fall to our death now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This place isn't going to collapse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, this is BABE itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have access to all areas\Nof BABE from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can certainly stop it from here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For a second there, I could feel\Nthe Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What we see here is just a husk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a trace of anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The data has been wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is left for us to see is an shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE surrendered and wiped\Nthe data on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that BABE has been shut down,\NTogetsu is no longer a threat to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I doubt they would give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but at least now we can confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no information\Nwe can extract from this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an empty husk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The communication is back online.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which can only mean BABE has been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you managed to stop BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have detected more anomalies\Nof the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening a little too frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We put an end to Togetsu's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the data here have been wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have found some useful information\Nabout the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, Kyoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are there any other places that store\Nresearch data or someone who knows them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Strings are power full of mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone has any\Ncomprehensive information about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there nothing we can do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is someone that can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She had the Red Strings\Nand she was your caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she had the knowledge\Nto raise Kasane into
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,someone capable of wielding\Nthe power of Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, she is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The quickest way is to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt that thing is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to use the Red Strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That is the only option we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that will exert more stress\Nto Yuito's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kunad Gate will keep expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The world will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the risk,\NI must try every option we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming here reminds me of so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could sense that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We will assist you with SAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an exact time and date\Nwhere you can meet Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's October 4th, 2009.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at an old OSF hospital of Lokusho City.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We can surely meet her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others attacked Lokusho City on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the day my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to recall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the time and place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But my memories about the past\Nare a little foggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you have us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown a little mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I should go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for the user of the Red Strings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone else will be sent back here\Nafter a certain amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the damages it could do\Nto your brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I must go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to let you\Ngo there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito was still young back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no telling what might happen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when two different you meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just an assumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but let's not take any risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Kasane go there alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With you who has the same power\Nstaying here in the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use you to find my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to act as a wayfinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you tried your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the children's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! There will be a feast tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a present for you too, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, before that, let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that boy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no signs of any changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But the process of treating Bell Peppers\Nvaries with each person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito really was a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you ready?\N-Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't go too far away.\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I received memories from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the memories, I saw you in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You proved the Red Strings' possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE's mainframe is connected to\Nthe brains of past Red Strings users.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,None was as powerful as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But BABE used those brains
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to trigger a phenomenon\Nsimilar to the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All the data were sent through time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to everyone who possessed the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The data were sent through time? Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain was found in the future BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, BABE's data were sent\Nback to the past to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I know you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown taller, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But now is not the time for nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know anything about the Kunad Gate,\Nplease tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is killing Yuito the only way\Nto close the Kunad Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Yuito lives, the Kunad Gate\Nwill eventually consume the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am already ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I must try at the moment\Nwhen the Red Strings was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to your timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NAll I need to do is take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a present for Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It took great effort to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This device will protect Yuito from\Nthe impact of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was originally used to mark\Nthe patients that needed specialized treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Yuito's earring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to swap this thing with\Nthe earring he's wearing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That should keep him safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(OTHER ALERT HAS BEEN ISSUED)\NOthers have been spotted in Lokusho City.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please evacuate to the nearest shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito!\N-Yuito, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The shelter is this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stay calm and move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Yuito inside the shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They came this far just to retrieve your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, look for Yuito inside the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look for him somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need you to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I don't have time to explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a gift from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hold it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop standing there, go to a shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take this child to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Jo Sumeragi's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, Yuito put on the earring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mom!\N-Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,WAKANA'S RESOLVE
